Thank you.

00:01.996 --> 00:02.457
Good morning.

00:03.518 --> 00:03.919
Good morning.

00:05.722 --> 00:10.810
It is lovely to see you all this morning, to see so many new faces as well, actually, it is wonderful, so welcome.

