I was saying to David earlier on that I had a 24-hour shift yesterday, which I got home at seven this morning, and I incidentally am preaching about wisdom, but made a massive, massive ever-in-judgment in not trying to swap out of that shift.

00:29.954 --> 00:33.000
Because I thought, oh, I'll be fine.

00:33.040 --> 00:35.284
I'll get home at nine o'clock in the evening and I'll sleep.

