03:26.530 --> 03:35.501
Daniel and three of his friends who were called Hananiah, Michelle and Azariah, who we would probably know more familiarly as Shadrach, Meshach and Abednego.

03:36.342 --> 03:41.068
And the various challenges and situations that they go through and how God is with them.

03:41.428 --> 03:47.496
